A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Chapter 29 of Title 50 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to
2 information technology relative to state government, so as to prohibit the use or installation
3 of any artificial intelligence system on state equipment when the company that developed or
4 deployed such artificial intelligence system is associated with the People's Republic of China;
5 to provide definitions; to provide for related matters; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other
6 purposes.
7 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
8 SECTION 1.
9 Chapter 29 of Title 50 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to information
10 technology relative to state government, is amended by adding a new article to read as
11 follows:
12 "ARTICLE 3
13 50-29-30.
14 As used in this article, the term:
S. B. 104
- 1 -

